data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled in the heart of Hemet! Ideally situated on a spacious corner lot within a coveted historic neighborhood, this residence offers an inviting blend of comfort and potential. Located just moments away from Weston Park, schools, a shopping center, and the bustling Downtown Village.    With its generous R2 Zone designation, the expansive lot presents numerous expansion possibilities, making it a versatile canvas for your future plans. Adding to its allure is the sizable detached garage, which has the potential to be converted into an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU), providing additional living space or income potential.    This residence offers three convenient entry points, including one into the kitchen, a second leading to the spacious upstairs bedroom, and a third granting access to a versatile living area, currently utilized as a 4th bedroom. The upstairs bedroom is a noteworthy feature, offering plumbing access for the potential addition of a third bathroom.    Don't miss the chance to make this home your own, with the opportunity to enhance and customize it to your heart's desire. Embrace the lifestyle and potential that this property in the heart of Hemet offers.
